snippet.title: DeathSprint 66 - Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Watch the lightning fast trailer for DeathSprint 66, an upcoming arcade racing game from Sumo Digital. Gore meets parkour in these eight-player PvP on-foot races. This is Earth's deadliest show.

DeathSprint 66 is coming to PC. It's available to wishlist now.

#IGN #Gaming #DeathSprint66
